Prosoma
. Length 8.9, width 6.7; carapace reddish-brown with genus-specific Union-Jack pattern; median light band largely restricted to around fovea, marginal light bands narrow (
Fig. 24A
); sternum light brown, covered with whitish setae (
Fig. 24C
).

